OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1778217986
OL,3,CFamily say they will continue search
OL,4,Cfor answers following death of their
OL,5,Cfather
OL,7,FThe family of a man who died two years
OL,8,Fago say they will continue their
OL,9,Fsearch for answers over the cause of
OL,10,Fhis death.
OL,12,FBill Trotter died at the Cumberland
OL,13,FInfirmary where his children say he
OL,14,Fwent through multiple misdiagnoses and
OL,15,Fnegligent treatment.
OL,17,FThe case has now been referred to the
OL,18,FAttorney General who will decide
OL,19,Fwhether an inquest will be held.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
