CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1778217986
OL,3,CFamily say they will continue search
OL,4,Cfor answers following death of their
OL,5,Cfather
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV Border, Bill Trotter's
OL,8,Fson, Michael Trotter said: "He wanted
OL,9,Fto be out of the hospital as fast as
OL,10,Fpossible as quite a few things he told
OL,11,Fus that were going on and dad was
OL,12,Fsharp as a very, very sharp individual.
OL,14,F"You could tell, there wasn't
OL,15,Fsomething quite right. And that's when
OL,16,Fwe found out about the uti urine
OL,17,Finfection.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1778217986
OL,3,CFamily say they will continue search
OL,4,Cfor answers following death of their
OL,5,Cfather
OL,7,F"And then obviously, we found out that
OL,8,Fhe was left with the full bladder for
OL,9,F16 days, which they actually done a
OL,10,Fscan in between that, which actually
OL,11,Fconfirmed that his bladder was
OL,12,Fsignificantly distended and that was
OL,13,Fignored for some reason.
OL,15,F"He was left for 16 days and he's
OL,16,Fscreaming, I want to die. I'm in pain."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1778217986
OL,3,CFamily say they will continue search
OL,4,Cfor answers following death of their
OL,5,Cfather
OL,7,FBill Trotter was admitted to the
OL,8,Fhospital due to an infection in his
OL,9,Ftoes, in the following weeks he was
OL,10,Fdiagnosed with gangrene and his leg
OL,11,Fwas amputated.
OL,13,FTwo days before he died, the family
OL,14,Fallege he was given insulin without
OL,15,Fthe knowledge of the hospital's
OL,16,Fdiabetes team, which the family say
OL,17,Fput him in a coma from which he never
OL,18,Fawoke.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
