OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1778217986
OL,3,CFamily say they will continue search
OL,4,Cfor answers following death of their
OL,5,Cfather
OL,7,FMichael Trotter said: "We have gone
OL,8,Fthrough every single organisation,
OL,9,Fworks with and around the trust,
OL,10,Fgovernment organisations to local
OL,11,Flevel, and there is no accountability
OL,12,Ffor families whatsoever.
OL,14,F"It's just the transparency. They all
OL,15,Fsay this open and honest transparency
OL,16,Fwhere we say we haven't seen any of
OL,17,Fit."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
