PN,35806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1778217986
OL,3,CFamily say they will continue search
OL,4,Cfor answers following death of their
OL,5,Cfather
OL,7,FCumbria's coroner rejected calls for
OL,8,Fan inquest, satisfied that Mr
OL,9,FTrotter's death was due to natural
OL,10,Fcauses.
OL,12,FFor Bill's daughter Kelly she said she
OL,13,Fwon't stop in her fight.
OL,15,FShe said: "I think the bottom line is
OL,16,Fto get that justice for me, dad, is
OL,17,Fwhat's keeping us going, because I
OL,18,Fthink he deserved it."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
