PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1778217986
OL,3,CFamily say they will continue search
OL,4,Cfor answers following death of their
OL,5,Cfather
OL,7,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for
OL,8,FNorth Cumbria Integrated Care said:
OL,9,F"The Trust has completed a full
OL,10,Fcomplaint investigation regarding Mr
OL,11,FTrotter's care.
OL,13,F"This process involved a thorough and
OL,14,Ftransparent review and the findings
OL,15,Fhave been shared in writing with the
OL,16,Ffamily addressing their concerns.
OL,26,@qD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1778217986
OL,3,CFamily say they will continue search
OL,4,Cfor answers following death of their
OL,5,Cfather
OL,7,F"Our investigation found that there
OL,8,Fwere no failings in care that
OL,9,Fcontributed to Mr Trotter's death. We
OL,10,Fare aware that other agencies have
OL,11,Falso examined aspects of this case.
OL,13,F"As the Trust's investigation is now
OL,14,Fconcluded, the family has been advised
OL,15,Fthat any further concerns should be
OL,16,Fdirected to the Public Health
OL,17,FOmbudsman."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/9
